title: War of the Roses: Kendra from Days Of Our Lives
description: Kelly and her boyfriend, Jacob, met a girl at a party who introduced herself as Kendra from Days Of Our Lives and afterwards Jacob said she was cute.  Jacob and Kendra built a friendship and even helped her put in a "backsplash" in her kitchen. He's also been forgetting his phone when he goes grocery shopping so now Kelly is thinking more than just a friendship is going on.
